high_descs: Turn around, go straight and then go to the dining table on your right.
Pick up the tomato closest to you on the dining table.
Turn around and go straight to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Pick up the knife inside the microwave.
Close the microwave.
Turn around and go straight to the sofa.
Cut the tomato on the sofa with the knife.
Go to the other part of the sofa containing a potato.
Put the knife on the sofa.
Go to the tomato on the sofa.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn around and go straight to the microwave.
Put the slice of the tomato inside the microwave.
Go towards the microwave on your left, turn right and go towards the dining table.
Pick up the tomato on the dining table, closest to you.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato in it.
Pick up the knife in the microwave.
Cut the tomato in the microwave and close it.
Turn around and go to the sofa with the knife.
Slice the tomato on the sofa.
Turn left, go straight and then turn left towards the sofa.
Put the knife on the side of the sofa that is closest to the chair.
Move towards the tomato on the sofa.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the sofa.
Turn around and head towards the microwave.
Keep the slice of the tomato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Keeping the tomatoes inside the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight ahead to the large dining table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the tomato nearest to you.
Turn around and go to the microwave ahead and against the wall on the right.
Put the tomato inside the microwave.
Remove the knife from the microwave.
Slice the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around and go towards the sofa.
Slice the tomato that's on the sofa.
Turn left to the end of the sofa.
Put the knife down.
Turn back towards the sliced tomato on the sofa.
Pick up one tomato slice.
Return to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a whole sliced apple and one more tomato slice in a microwave.
